{
  "1875810": {
    "name": "Slashers",
    "steam_appid": 1875810,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到猛击者！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/8152448764c5117933a59bdf4e87b6a7.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/8152448764c5117933a59bdf4e87b6a7.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/8152448764c5117933a59bdf4e87b6a7.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在Slashers中，一群年轻人总是会进入一个废弃的地方，你必须找到一种方法离开那里，但这并不容易，因为你总是会有一个杀人犯跟踪你。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >失物招领处</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/7c8a5933d19511fd1629539f8ccc9532.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/7c8a5933d19511fd1629539f8ccc9532.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/7c8a5933d19511fd1629539f8ccc9532.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在地图上随机找到物体，这些将作为拼图，以适合其他碎片并削弱敌人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随机性</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/97bf30d9058fce03f6f9f625bf56972f.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/97bf30d9058fce03f6f9f625bf56972f.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/97bf30d9058fce03f6f9f625bf56972f.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每次玩新游戏时，地图的许多元素（例如物体）都是完全随机的，敌人是不可预测的，并且在前往某些地方时不会遵循准则。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逃跑或战斗</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/e34d7b63fa353d7bcd8dbf9561dcee87.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/e34d7b63fa353d7bcd8dbf9561dcee87.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/e34d7b63fa353d7bcd8dbf9561dcee87.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你可以尝试逃离敌人或与他战斗，地图上有几个物体可以用来击中敌人并击晕他，这对于拯救朋友很有用。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >避免被抓住</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/d1935cf6ef1198ca959d65a8a22a9755.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/d1935cf6ef1198ca959d65a8a22a9755.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/d1935cf6ef1198ca959d65a8a22a9755.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>如果你被抓住，他们会把你锁在你的朋友可以在某些情况下救你或你自己的区域，如果每个人都被困住，你将转向另一个不需要的形式。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完成仪式</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/0d78eb2e2d9f63eec6a30d96f1a646ed.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/0d78eb2e2d9f63eec6a30d96f1a646ed.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/0d78eb2e2d9f63eec6a30d96f1a646ed.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>找到各种元素将它们放入碎片中，以削弱和击败敌人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不要独自一人在黑暗中</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/3011892ef0f383ea93fb0ac50084303d.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=219 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/3011892ef0f383ea93fb0ac50084303d.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>当心孤独和黑暗，你呆的时间越长，你就越会被建议，你会开始听到声音，事情就会开始发生。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >控制手电筒</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/4d2a043de542faefe3f92861e9992b9b.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/4d2a043de542faefe3f92861e9992b9b.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/4d2a043de542faefe3f92861e9992b9b.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>电池电量耗尽，这会导致您越来越不强烈地看到，请用新电池保持手电筒充电。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >当心噪音</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/35c49a0bcb7fa150ca45cc4e18525d4a.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/35c49a0bcb7fa150ca45cc4e18525d4a.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/35c49a0bcb7fa150ca45cc4e18525d4a.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>声音和互动吸引敌人，控制麦克风发出的噪音和你所做的动作，如果伴侣尖叫，他们可以在中间抓住你。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >管理耐力</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/7cd237ae2016408aec167b46066db75f.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=219 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/7cd237ae2016408aec167b46066db75f.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>你可能会发现自己处于角落的境地，只有当你能跑的时候才能救你，耗尽耐力可能是致命的。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在光线下采取预防措施</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/e5c34eba80f38ace6a1e82927accd50a.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/e5c34eba80f38ace6a1e82927accd50a.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/e5c34eba80f38ace6a1e82927accd50a.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>光线会让你从偏执中恢复过来，但它也可以成为吸引敌人的完美焦点，利用它来发挥你的优势，但要小心。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >管理片段</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/998f30e1f0e41e915c7ef9f212908c37.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/998f30e1f0e41e915c7ef9f212908c37.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/998f30e1f0e41e915c7ef9f212908c37.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>放置碎片需要一段时间，保持一致并在敌人抓住你之前进行管理。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >保持警觉</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/059746be76a580e18f8c399a8e9d8a93.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/059746be76a580e18f8c399a8e9d8a93.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/059746be76a580e18f8c399a8e9d8a93.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>敌人将关闭/打开电源，打开/关闭门，移除/添加汽油到发电机。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >聆听声音</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/aebe0b864343330769d65379f33a19dc.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/aebe0b864343330769d65379f33a19dc.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/aebe0b864343330769d65379f33a19dc.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>敌人去找人时总会发出特有的声音，如果那个人就是你，你总会听到紧张的音乐，如果它消失了，就意味着它已经停止了追逐你。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收集</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/64e1994b07de02a3608d6aed8ab87673.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/64e1994b07de02a3608d6aed8ab87673.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/64e1994b07de02a3608d6aed8ab87673.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>地图上总会有收藏品，你可以单独找到，其中一些非常隐蔽，而另一些则不是，你需要拿走它们才能显示下一个。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >视觉</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/1c75e7bdc94bb2f07f64db9f610e1d61.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/1c75e7bdc94bb2f07f64db9f610e1d61.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/1c75e7bdc94bb2f07f64db9f610e1d61.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>敌人很难在黑暗中看到，在阴影中玩耍，并避免光发射，这样他们就不会被发现。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >阶段</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/edde36b104a6b70198eb21d60644717b.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/edde36b104a6b70198eb21d60644717b.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/edde36b104a6b70198eb21d60644717b.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每放置一个碎片都会削弱敌人，但它会变得更强、更大、更快、更具侵略性。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >聪明</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/8ea8dfd016e2621099d0991ca8401005.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/8ea8dfd016e2621099d0991ca8401005.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/8ea8dfd016e2621099d0991ca8401005.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>指出你在某些情况下需要的物品，这些物品将始终被所有玩家看到。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >模式</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/53a3e0a54bbfa46980a611350cec581b.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/53a3e0a54bbfa46980a611350cec581b.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/53a3e0a54bbfa46980a611350cec581b.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Slashers的特点是拥有各种游戏模式，其中一些正在开发中，另一些将一点一点地出现（经典，逃脱，Slashers，疯狂和转弯）。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可重玩性</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/4b5fed6a5fa15b8772e1cf1222e9ea7f.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/4b5fed6a5fa15b8772e1cf1222e9ea7f.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/4b5fed6a5fa15b8772e1cf1222e9ea7f.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏被设计为无限次重玩，因此每个帐篷，物体，海报都将随机出现或随机生成。<br>你还将在玩游戏时解锁困难，这将增加你必须获得的碎片数量，敌人将达到新的阶段。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >支持我們</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/3cddd62f8bcbd2ff7320c62ababd9e66.poster.avif?t=1743717353\" width=616 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/3cddd62f8bcbd2ff7320c62ababd9e66.webm?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875810/extras/3cddd62f8bcbd2ff7320c62ababd9e66.mp4?t=1743717353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>我們需要積極的評論，我們依靠我們的網站來更新和改進我們的遊戲，您可以看到我們在路線圖中提出的所有改進。",
